# Yarnoodle AI Blog Automation

## .env Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values

# OpenAI API
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Website Publishing (Static HTML Export)
WEBSITE_OUTPUT_DIR=../generated_posts

# Custom REST API (optional)
WEBSITE_API=https://your-site.com/api
WEBSITE_TOKEN=your-bearer-token

# WordPress (optional)
WORDPRESS_URL=https://your-wordpress-site.com
WORDPRESS_USERNAME=your-username
WORDPRESS_PASSWORD=your-application-password

# Pinterest Profile URL
PINTEREST_PROFILE_URL=https://www.pinterest.com/YarnoodleAmigurumi/_created/

# Publisher Mode: static | wordpress | api
PUBLISHER_MODE=static

# AI Model
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o

# Scheduler time (24h format)
SCHEDULE_TIME=09:00

# Posts per page limit
POSTS_PER_DAY=1
